                    <div class="TestimonialText MarginBottomMediumTexts">
                        <p><em>“HR Tech World Amsterdam will be our biggest yet with 5000 attendees and we are excited to be returning to the city where our show was first produced” said <span class="AmsterdamColor"> Marc Coleman, Founder and CEO of HR Tech World.</span> “We’ve brought in a number of business visionaries over the years including Sir Richard Branson, Gary Vaynerchuk, Sir Ken Robinson and more and have created an equally impressive agenda that will inspire attendees to unleash their people’s potential in the workplace.” </em></p>
                    </div>
